<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7883c825-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s715k–4"><num value="715k–4">§ 715k–4.</num><heading> Accounting and use of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Funds appropriated each fiscal year pursuant to sections 715k–3 to 715k–5 of this title shall be accounted for, added to, and used for purposes of the migratory bird conservation fund <ref class="footnoteRef" idref="fn002494">1</ref><note type="footnote" id="fn002494"><num>1</num> So in original. Probably should be capitalized.</note> established pursuant to <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s718d">section 718d of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7883c826-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/87/383/s2">Pub. L. 87–383, § 2</ref>, <date date="1961-10-04">Oct. 4, 1961</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/75/813">75 Stat. 813</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id7883c827-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id7883c828-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id7883c829-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was not enacted as part of the Migratory Bird Conservation Act which comprises this subchapter.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
